In order to compile the program the following files:
tHeader.cpp
tHeader.h
server.cpp 
must be on afsaccess1.njit.edu

and the following files:
tHeader.cpp
tHeader.h
client.cpp 
much be on another machine.(e.g afsaccess2)
.
.
.
.			
Compile server with command: 
g++ -std=c++0x tHeader.cpp server.cpp
.
.
.
.								
Compile client on a different machine with command:
g++ -std=c++0x tHeader.cpp client.cpp
.
.
.
Run the server first using command: 
./a.out
then the client with the same command.
